//BASIC SCAN
COMMAND - lbd <target site>

//Advanced Scan
COMMAND - lbd <target site> port server

//EXAMPLE - lbd google.com 443 https(target site is google, port specified is 443 which is open and https server is there)

//DESCRIPTION - It is a tool which is used to detect whether the load balancing is enabled in a ip/domain or not.

To get more information about the fierce tool type any of the following 2 commands :
*lbd -h 
*lbd --help
[ Both -h and --help will give the same results :) ]
